{"tid":745200,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本「爸爸銀行」免費出租臨時爸爸　給單親家庭小朋友一點溫暖","createTime":"2018-07-16T14:21:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-17T00:47:27.000Z","uid":53304,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"270278a8ba0d79c4e55c1499c1f997cbf94c3e15","tid":745200,"uid":53304,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:21:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2108503/japan_thumb_20180710_ch_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2108503%2Fjapan_thumb_20180710_ch_1024.jpg&h=54809a55&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n日本最近出現了「爸爸銀行」，免費出租爸爸，代陪單親孩子玩樂。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現代人工作忙碌，經常無暇陪伴孩子，對一些身兼父職的單親媽媽來説，既要兼顧工作，又要照顧孩子，便更是吃力。日本最近就出現了「爸爸銀行」，為有需要的家庭提供「臨時爸爸」的服務。<br />\n<br />\n「爸爸銀行」供喜歡照顧小孩的男士報名，他們大多都擅長DIY、烹飪、玩紙板等不同活動。在網站註冊後，他們會被編入「爸爸圖鑒」，家長可通過Facebook等平台委託他們幫忙，由於「臨時爸爸」的是義工性質，因此費用全免。<br />\n<br />\n「臨時爸爸」的服務多元，包括在家陪伴孩子畫畫、帶孩子到戶外玩樂、參加學校運動會為孩子打氣、出席家長會等等。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2108503/22728767_817042531799943_457451155956200563_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2108503%2F22728767_817042531799943_457451155956200563_n_1024.jpg&h=0087327c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n與小朋友去長野縣一起登山。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2108503/22730351_817042635133266_4477977880468082047_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2108503%2F22730351_817042635133266_4477977880468082047_n_1024.jpg&h=f4ed75c6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n和孩子觀賞風景。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n40歲的豐田泰生是一家兒童巴西柔術培訓班的老闆，也是11歲小六學生真田陽花的「臨時爸爸」。今年5月，他和另一位男士受到陽花媽媽的委託，以父親身分出席陽花學校的運動會，並為參加比賽的她準備便當、拍照和加油助威等。豐田表示「本來就喜歡看見小孩高興的樣子」，陽花的母親美雪亦覺得很熱鬧，人多點更好玩。<br />\n<br />\n「爸爸銀行」創始人義廣千秋表示，喜歡小孩的人都可以註冊成為「臨時爸爸」，女性如果有意也可以註冊，但在註冊之前雙方必須進行面談。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://topick.hket.com/res/v3/image/content/2105000/2108503/36350003_943975992439929_4374303489510080512_n_1024.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Fres%2Fv3%2Fimage%2Fcontent%2F2105000%2F2108503%2F36350003_943975992439929_4374303489510080512_n_1024.jpg&h=a40b400e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n附近有大自然環境、聽着蟲叫及流水聲，與小朋友舒服地玩樂，像活在烏托邦的世界。（資料圖片）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n男保姆需求亦增<br />\n<br />\n除了「臨時爸爸」，日本對男保姆的需求也越來越高。30歲的男保姆吉野一真平時是一名格鬥家和教練，他喜歡戶外活動，因此經常陪孩子爬樹、玩躲避球、籃球、到野外露營。男保姆的出現，亦解決了父母無暇陪伴孩子玩樂的難題。<br />\n<br />\nLink: <a href=\"https://topick.hket.com/article/2108503/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftopick.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2108503%2F&d=592NbAX12gRHz7hn00hMX0kviAvgRC9mxyv2vFgVDqU%3D&h=9f0cb7c8\" target=\"_blank\">https://topick.hket.com/article/2108503/</a>"},{"pid":"c2b78145de3594eef3d5d7676fc64ca37aef281c","tid":745200,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:24:37.000Z","msg":"有無出租媽媽 需要愛個隻"},{"pid":"2f7df863e520947e0621ec225963be6d8028dab6","tid":745200,"uid":1672,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T14:36:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/07/16/223637_9bccf06d0573ae5865eafde2beec09e1.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F07%2F16%2F223637_9bccf06d0573ae5865eafde2beec09e1.png&h=fd9c93f8&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"82b290ea82c8f99a7bbc5221cd0e6ba2ce4d2c03","tid":745200,"uid":82450,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T15:27:43.000Z","msg":"出租鬼父<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"41b5d6185e0c29e83dabfd6c4a33a2f024e11e46","tid":745200,"uid":51701,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T15:28:41.000Z","msg":"出租老公<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{